TITLE: Implementing Prototype Inheritance in JavaScript with Person and Student Classes
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines Person and Student classes using prototype-based inheritance. The Person class has an age property and a getAge method, while the Student class extends Person and adds a grade property and getGrade method. It demonstrates how to set up the prototype chain and use the call method for proper inheritance.
